          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">⭐ 4.9-Star Reviews</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">💰 Deep Cleans from $175</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">🏠 AL &amp; TN Service</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">🛡️ $2M Insured</span>
