        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          We're not saying you need to hire someone. We're saying you need to honestly count what your current situation is costing you. Make the decision with clear eyes.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Because a clean home isn't a luxury. It's not something you "should" be able to handle yourself. It's a foundation for everything else in your life—your health, your relationships, your mental state, your productivity.
        </p>

